Package: socialsurvey
Title: R Functions for Social Survey Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Sho", "Fujihara", , "fujihara@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of R functions for social survey data analysis.
    Includes tools for frequency tables, metadata management, variable labels,
    value labels, and codebook generation. Supports Stata, SPSS, and SAS files.
